  "title": "WELFARE OFFICER",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Location:  Muhammadiyah Welfare Home 101 Pasir Ris Road, Singapore 519154</strong></h3>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em>Please send your resume to hr@muhammadiyah.org.sg</em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities :</strong></p>\n<p>• To supervise residents on their daily routine in the home.</p>\n<p>• To ensure safety, welfare and confidentiality of the residents is being safeguarded at all times.</p>\n<p>• To supervise and ensure smooth execution of residents’ daily routine and programme.</p>\n<p>• To ensure proper housekeeping at all times.</p>\n<p>• To perform secondary duty as and when required.</p>\n<p>• To perform any other relevant duties as delegated by supervisor.</p>\n<p>• *Residents – boys between the age of 11 to 19 years old</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements/Qualifications :</strong></p>\n<p>• Minimum GCE N level or equivalent qualification/ relevant experience.</p>\n<p>• Physically fit.</p>\n<p>• Able to manage and educate at-risk youths.</p>\n<p>• Able to work on shifts.</p>",
